description:
"This new year, give yourself Moodlytics - A gift for Happiness! It will lead your life from sadness to happiness. It has already changed many of our users' lives!"

It's not an App, It's Companion for Happiness.

What is Moodlytics?
• Moodlytics is a platform comprising of your Moods and its Analytics. It's a Mood Tracker App, which allows you to log your moods and track them periodically through graphs, charts and calendars. In other words its sort of Mood Journal or a Mood Diary.

Why Moodlytics?
• The more you log your moods, the better you build your mood journal. Stronger your mood journal is, the better tracking and analysis you can perform. Thus conclusively moodlytics helps you to log your moods, maintain a mood journal, track your moods through charts, calendars and graphs and perform a deep analysis for "Happiness"

• Apart from rich user interface and best visuals, its the following features that makes us more better and stronger than some of the already existing apps like T2 Mood tracker,Moody Me Mood Diary and Tracker, Mood Analyzer, Mood kit, Mood Detector, MyMood Tracker, e Moods Bipolar Mood Tracker, IMood Journal, Mood Scanner, Mood Tracker - Depression, Period Tracker, Mood Panda - Mood Diary and Tracker etc.

Features:
- Log current moods & past moods
- Moods are represented with scientific colours
- 42 cute mood smiles, best in class
- Add notes, photos & people to moods
- Track & Analyse Mood journal through Charts and Calendars (Better Visuals)
- Best in class Mood and happiness analysis
- Set Mood Logger reminders & Profiles
- Log moods once a day with Scheduled Reminder
- Now set Simple as well as MoodSensed Goals
- Add & Personalise moods
- Export Mood data to PDF and share via email
- Backup & Restore your mood data
- Privacy features to prevent unauthorised access
- MoodPedia - A mood encyclopaedia
- Share your moods on Facebook and Twitter
